name: Where Do I Go At Night?
name_original: Where Do I Go At Night?
description:
A short interactive fiction of a woman who is taken inexpleciably to a mysterious darkened mansion each night.  This is just an introductory chapter, there is a possibility I could add more, however unlikely. Perhaps if I figure out where to take the story

Made for UntitledGameJam #46

Controls with arrow keys
